title: From Churchin' To Trappin'
itunes:title: From Churchin' To Trappin'
description:
WED 10/19 - Jeezy stops by The Breakfast Club to talk about his new album "Trap or Die 3", why he reverted back to that series after "Church in These Streets", his role in the B.M.F. TV series, successfully guiding YG's career and more!
